00:00:01,279 --> 00:00:03,079
Lesson 93.

2
00:00:03,899 --> 00:00:05,479
Our new neighbour.

3
00:00:06,099 --> 00:00:10,080
Listen to the tape, then answer this question.

4
00:00:12,419 --> 00:00:15,380
Why is Nigel a lucky man?

5
00:00:17,699 --> 00:00:20,359
Nigel is our new next-door neighbour.

6
00:00:20,820 --> 00:00:21,940
He's a pilot.

7
00:00:22,379 --> 00:00:24,679
He was in the RAF.

8
00:00:25,219 --> 00:00:27,459
He will fly to New York next month.

9
00:00:27,559 --> 00:00:31,519
The month after next, he'll fly to Tokyo.

10
00:00:32,179 --> 00:00:34,699
At the moment, he's in Madrid.

11
00:00:35,420 --> 00:00:37,779
He flew to Spain a week ago.

12
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:41,359
He'll return to London the week after next.

13
00:00:42,299 --> 00:00:49,140
He's only 41 years old, and he has already been to nearly every country in the world.

14
00:00:50,020 --> 00:00:52,839
Nigel is a very lucky man.

15
00:00:53,259 --> 00:00:54,979
But his wife isn't very lucky.

16
00:00:55,079 --> 00:00:58,159
She usually stays at home.

